  "subject": "aai/aai-service: Fixing site path for nexus",
  "commit_message": "aai/aai-service: Fixing site path for nexus\n\npom.xml specifies the wrong site url where the site:stage-deploy\nneeds to happen.\nThe site path in nexus to post to should match the repo name.\nIn this case, \"content/sites/site/org.openecomp.aai.aai-service/\"\n\nChange-Id: I43e384f9be48c128b007a41e74b34032136e1efc\nSigned-off-by: Jessica Wagantall <jwagantall@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
